Project Information
-------------------

Project Name:
    OpenStream

Description:
    OpenStream is a modern Android streaming platform built with
    Kotlin, Jetpack Compose, and modern Android architecture principles.

Core Technologies:
    - Kotlin
    - Jetpack Compose
    - Media3 / ExoPlayer
    - Room Database
    - Retrofit / OkHttp
    - Coroutines
    - Clean Architecture

Repository Purpose:
    Educational, experimental, and development-focused streaming platform.

